nodes.text: Hi,  This is Person1, Person2 daughter. My husband was just diagnosed with skin cancer by his dermatologist. I am trying to get the biopsy report now from Dr  Person3. They want him to come back and have more of it removed would like him to see Dr Person4 but not sure how quickly he could get in? I will try calling too looking for advice. Thank you, Person5
